T02D2954:33a-0: @33a * // dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2954:33a-1: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du
T02D2954:33a-2: dbang bskur bar 'dod pa'i sgrub pa po dam tshig
T02D2954:33a-3: dang ldan pas gnas khang yid dang mthun par me
T02D2954:33a-4: tog sil ma bkram la sa chog la sogs pa
T02D2954:33a-5: sngon du song bas rgyu skar rnams kyi dkyil 'khor
T02D2954:33a-6: bzhengs te dbus padma 'dab brgyad la dkar po lte
T02D2954:33a-7: ba sngon po / mu khyud padma'i phreng bas mdzes par bskor ba /
T02D2954:33a-8: khyams dar dmar po la shar nas brtsams nas sna
T02D2954:33a-9: tshogs yid du 'ong ba'i khang bu bdun bdun gyis
T02D2954:33a-10: bskor bsgo bzhi mu khyud sna tshogs skar ma'i 'od
T02D2954:33a-11: 'khrug pa bri'o // de nas gtso bo'i mtshan ma dang /
T02D2954:33a-12: padma rnams la gza' brgyad kyi mtshan ma dang /
T02D2954:33a-13: khang bu rnams su shar nas brtsams te /
T02D2954:33b-18: sin dh'u ra'i sol ba dang ;
T02D2954:33b-25: rma bya rnams bri bar bya'o //
T02D2954:33b-26: de nas bum pa nyi shu rtsa dgu la rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02D2954:33b-27: so so'i mtshan ma dri sna tshogs pas btab la /
T02D2954:33b-29: phyogs mtshams rnams su phur bus 'khor bar gzhag go //
T02D2954:33b-30: de dag gi bar bar du'ang tshon sna tshogs pa'i skud pas sbrel lo //
T02D2954:33b-31: bdug spos la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i yo byad ci 'byor pa bsham mo //
T02D2954:33b-32: de nas gza' dang rgyu skar gyi gtor ma dang /
T02D2954:33b-33: phyogs skyong rnams la gtor ma tshul bzhin du bsham mo //

T02D2954:33b-35: so so'i bum par sngags dang phyag rgyas bskyed do
T02D2954:33b-36: // shar gyi bum pa dang po nas brtsams te
T02D2954:33b-37: smin drug dkar po zhal gcig phyag stong dang ldan
T02D2954:33b-38: pa phyag g-yas nam dung bsnams pa /
T02D2954:33b-39: zhal nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun 'bab pa /
T02D2954:33b-40: khyi dkar po la zhon pa bskyed do //
T02D2954:33b-41: de bzhin du gzhan 'dra ba la snar ma mdog
T02D2954:33b-42: ser ljang phyag na mda' bo che nya la zhon
T02D2954:33b-43: pa / mgo mdog dkar smug 'khor lo sre mo la zhon pa /
T02D2954:33b-44: lag mdog dkar gtun shing bsnams pa glang la zhon pa /
T02D2954:33b-45: nab so mdog dkar po phyag na phub ba lang la zhon pa /

T02D2954:33b-47: skag sngon po rnga yab bsnams pa rtal zhon pa bskyed do //
T02D2954:33b-48: lho phyogs su mchu mdog ser pa lag pa brgya
T02D2954:33b-49: stong grangs med pa rin po che'i rgyan rnams kyis
T02D2954:33b-50: brgyan pa / phyag rnams na me bsnams pa bya la zhon ba bskyed do //
T02D2954:33b-51: gre mdog sngo skya phyag na chu /
T02D2954:33b-53: dbo mdog dmar skya phyag rnams nas /

T02D2954:33b-56: rin po che sna bzhi'i khri la gnas pa /
T02D2954:33b-57: nag pa mdog nag po phyag rnams na rgyal mtshan g-yag la zhon pa /
T02D2954:33b-58: sa ri mdog ser po phyag na sbud pa /
T02D2954:33b-59: gser gyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
T02D2954:34a-0: sa ga mdog dud ka phyag rnams @34a * //
T02D2954:34a-2: sbrul la zhon pa bskyed do //

T02D2954:34a-30: phyag brgya stong na rma bya sngon po bsnams pa /
T02D2954:34a-31: zhal gcig pa zhal nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun 'bab pa rus sbal zhon pa bskyed do //

T02D2954:34a-33: zer brgya stong dpag tu med pa 'phro ba bskyed
T02D2954:34a-34: do // sngags ni aom sa sv'a h'a /
